{
  "info": {
    "name": "BX Finance — 3-Token Delegated Chain (may_act / RFC 8693)",
    "description": "Tests the full 3-token delegation chain:\n\n1. **Subject Token** - Authorization Code + PKCE as real API calls:\n   - **Step 1a** GETs `/authorize` — pre-request generates PKCE params and logs the full authorization URL to the Postman console. Open that URL in your browser, log in, copy the `code=` value from the callback redirect, paste it into the `auth_code` collection variable.\n   - **Step 1b** POSTs to `/token` to exchange the code for the Subject Token. Carries `may_act.sub = PINGONE_CORE_CLIENT_ID`.\n2. **MCP Token** - RFC 8693 Token Exchange #1. Banking App exchanges the Subject Token for an MCP-scoped token.\n3. **PingOne API Token** - Client Credentials from BX Finance MCP Service. Used to call the PingOne Management API.\n4. **User Lookup** - GET /users/{sub} using Token 3, proving the full chain works end-to-end.\n\n## Setup\nImport this collection, then set these **Collection Variables** (gear icon -> Edit -> Variables):\n\n| Variable | Where to find it |\n|---|---|\n| `PINGONE_ENVIRONMENT_ID` | PingOne Console -> Environment -> Settings |\n| `PINGONE_REGION` | `com` (US) or `eu` / `ca` / `ap` |\n| `PINGONE_CORE_USER_CLIENT_ID` | Client ID of **BX Finance User** app |\n| `PINGONE_CORE_CLIENT_ID` | Client ID of **BX Finance Banking App** |\n| `PINGONE_CORE_CLIENT_SECRET` | Client Secret of **BX Finance Banking App** |\n| `MCP_CLIENT_ID` | Client ID of **BX Finance MCP Service** |\n| `MCP_CLIENT_SECRET` | Client Secret of **BX Finance MCP Service** |\n\n## Running the chain\nRun all steps in order: **1a -> 1b -> 2 -> 3 -> 4**.\nAll token variables (`subject_token`, `mcp_token`, `pingone_api_token`, `user_sub`) are auto-populated by the test scripts.\n\n**Redirect URI:** Add `https://oauth.pstmn.io/v1/callback` as a Redirect URI on the BX Finance User app before running Step 1a.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "PINGONE_ENVIRONMENT_ID",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Your PingOne environment UUID"
    },
    {
      "key": "PINGONE_REGION",
      "value": "com",
      "description": "com | eu | ca | ap"
    },
    {
      "key": "PINGONE_CORE_USER_CLIENT_ID",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Client ID — BX Finance User app"
    },
    {
      "key": "PINGONE_CORE_CLIENT_ID",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Client ID — BX Finance Banking App"
    },
    {
      "key": "PINGONE_CORE_CLIENT_SECRET",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Client Secret — BX Finance Banking App"
    },
    {
      "key": "MCP_CLIENT_ID",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Client ID — BX Finance MCP Service"
    },
    {
      "key": "MCP_CLIENT_SECRET",
